### Scripts and commands

- **Root scripts**: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
  - Delegated via Turbo: `test`, `test-coverage`, `build`, `type-check`, `lint`
  - Preferred entrypoints when operating across the monorepo

- **Package scripts**:
  - Core: [durable-execution/package.json](mdc:durable-execution/package.json)
  - Storage: [storage-drizzle/package.json](mdc:storage-drizzle/package.json)
  - Common:
    - `test`: `vitest run`
    - `test-coverage`: `vitest run --coverage`
    - `build`: `tsup`

- **Usage tips**:
  - Use root scripts to run all packages; use `-F <pkg>` to scope to one package
  - CI expects `pnpm test-coverage` at root to produce per-package coverage outputs
